  "prompt": "Who are the Impractical Jokers?",
  "response": "The Impractical Jokers are a comedy troupe consisting of four members: Joe Gatto, James \"Murr\" Murray, Brian \"Q\" Quinn, and Sal Vulcano. They are known for their hidden camera prank show, \"Impractical Jokers,\" which premiered on TruTV in December 2011. On the show, the quartet often engages in outrageous challenges and practical jokes on one another, typically in public places, with the goal of embarrassing each other. Their unique blend of humor, camaraderie, and improvisation has garnered them a substantial fan base and various spin-offs, live tours, and specials.",
